{"tid":1628581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[更正] 前線受養者注意","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:29:41.000Z","uid":83015,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f43b3edfeddb92e82ac41d106799fcd94aa79a0d","tid":1628581,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"*之前編文打錯受養者同助養者<br />\n<br />\n各位，<br />\n我收到admin谷討論了一部份助養前線情況<br />\n發覺有疑似偽手足與助養channel溝通，想資助學費。係交談之間，疑似被騙下數百以至數萬資金。<br />\n因數目比較大，擔心影響其他需要捐助者需要，特此通告要求：<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: red;\">受養者</span>盡量不要用學費買文具，如聲稱學費困難問題，channel不排除向<span style=\"color: red;\">受養者</span>要求直接取得學費入數紙或通告，同意<span style=\"color: red;\">channel方/助養方</span>有權直接處理而不經<span style=\"color: red;\">受養者</span>處理<br />\n2) 有困難者，文具可向國難，香港自由之書，hktvmall, amazon (優先) 申請，<br />\n而另有<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/BTReptile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FBTReptile&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=f9c213d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/BTReptile</a> @wearenoone 可直接購買<br />\n3) 如<span style=\"color: red;\">受養者</span>因急需文具而用了食飯錢買文具，建議申請飯票/卷/飯堂資助<br />\n使用飯票飯堂等助養，更少減輕其他資助壓力。<br />\n<br />\n另外，文具channel ppe助養有資金困難<br />\n請轉移到其他channel 助養<br />\n*****************<br />\n另外， 棄文具時，放在容易辨識，近民居的地方，例如屋苑閘口/欄，次選巴士站頂，草叢或樹枝<br />\n<br />\n屋苑黃絲支持者建議臨時收藏文具，等下次會放在游行路線等人自取，至少幫到大家"},{"pid":"2bd3100e9dfc1410250bac130f54eff569295ddb","tid":1628581,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"小心d批好 好多貪心狗 推"},{"pid":"a575aba5d2f9a269b2acbae9c522ae0e85fbef9f","tid":1628581,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"另外，文具channel ppe助養有資金困難<br />\n請轉移到其他channel <span style=\"color: red;\">受養</span><br />\n<br />\n成日打錯字"},{"pid":"093ed7e0a32d82466baab871f570a982e2330b27","tid":1628581,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a0f01ff605f3fd8a00f6f8afff8b3d3133b770","tid":1628581,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"希望無打錯字"}]}